   1  """ 
   2  `auibar.py` contains an implementation of :class:`AuiToolBar`, which is a completely owner-drawn 
   3  toolbar perfectly integrated with the AUI layout system. This allows drag and drop of 
   4  toolbars, docking/floating behaviour and the possibility to define "overflow" items 
   5  in the toolbar itself. 
   6   
   7  The default theme that is used is :class:`AuiToolBar`, which provides a modern, 
   8  glossy look and feel. The theme can be changed by calling :meth:`AuiToolBar.SetArtProvider`. 
   9  """
